Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.10,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be able to catch up to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I can, what am I going to say to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have any right to stop Misaki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, are you sightseeing at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pitch-dark, so you won't be able to see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... that is... I'm meeting up with a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,At that cape?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the construction has been completed,\Nso I guess there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}("Misaki" = "Promontory" in Japanese)\N3 lshihama Misaki Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:37.25,TL,,0,0,0,,Don't waste the only life you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I pass her somewhere along the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Or... don't tell me... she already...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know which train Misaki-chan took\Nfrom the timetable left at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I paid extra for the express train and chased her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I shouldn't be able to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Was my outlook too optimistic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Misaki-chan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-kun and I only arrived five minutes apart of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-kun, you could become a detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You found out even though I kept it a secret from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go back. It's cold out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't die. You have to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw around! I wasted the earnings\Nfrom my part-time job because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have died properly last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly as my stepfather told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone becomes unhappy if I'm around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm to blame for my mother's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My biological father's death was probably my fault, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Although my stepfather was determined to get\Nrid of me, he failed, and predictably, his luck went bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I helped my aunt with her solicitation work, she began\Nto struggle and started arguing with my uncle on a frequent basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a pathetic human failure who only brings unhappiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm someone who isn't wanted in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I didn't want to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the project was conceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:05:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as there was one person who needed me...\Nthe words of my stepfather would have been lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have given me a reason to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the project ended in failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Satou-kun needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no purpose in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the reason for the mikka tororo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play games with me! That note\Nhad "come after me" written all over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to find it, Satou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought my heart was\Ngoing to stop when I saw you here, Satou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't have mattered if it did, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, a suicide note is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a note, people wouldn't be able to discern whether it\Nwas a suicide or not, further inconveniencing those left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Like in the case of my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good things will come from living!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uncle and aunt will be sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I... er, need Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You say the strangest things, Satou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any words to stop Misaki-chan with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, what's so bad about dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The only difference is whether it happens sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly as Misaki-chan said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you continue to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a struggle full of hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no meaning to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no meaning in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But... you definitely can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say you're going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Satou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike the others, I can't believe in God,\Nsince I have a poor imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If an extravagant miracle would occur\Nbefore my eyes, like in the Bible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I could blame all the bad things on God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, Misaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-chan, you're not to blame at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else is responsible for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone who's causing Misaki-chan misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Why would there be any reason for Misaki-chan to suffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be ridiculous to say Misaki-chan was meant to be lonely and in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the source must exist somewhere out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an evil entity inflicting pain upon Misaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know conspiracies do exist in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:09:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However, ninety-nine percent of all conspiracy\Ntheories are simply delusions... or blatant lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... does that make the remaining one percent legitimate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Misaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Somebody has, against extreme odds,\Nbecome aware of a genuine conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou Tatsuhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's the name of the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known the name... for a longtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The evil organization that has been torturing us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,N.H.K.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,NHK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The name is N.H.K.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,An evil, secret society encompassing the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The unfortunate incidents occurring around\Nyou are the work of the N.H.K., Misaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-kun, what are you sayi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mind attack by the N.H.K.!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They've come to finish me off since I told you\Nthe secret of their organization, Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What does N.H.K. stand for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nihon Hikikomori Kyokai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The evil, secret society that transformed me into a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffff80&\an8}Note: Hiyowa translates to "weakling",\NHikan translates to "pessimist".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it's the Nihon Hiyowa Kyokai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking advantage of senpai's weak mind and\Nmaking her participate in an offline suicide meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-chan, the N.H.K.'s sinister clutches are even after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In your case, the Nihon Hikan Kyokai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the ones responsible for forcing Misaki-chan\Ninto thinking pessimistically about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single bad thing that occurs in this\Nworld is due to the N.H.K.'s conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call it whatever you like if you don't like the sound of "N.H.K.".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:11:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so they've come to deliver the final blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see it, Misaki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see it! Carefully fix your eyes on what lies ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! I can't see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes you can! You can definitely see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the source of all evil... the last boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for me. I'm not going to die in vain, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take it down with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only thing that can defeat it, the revolution bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. In order to defeat it, I have to use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to carry out a suicide attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Live a healthy life from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Live a happy life, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are my last wishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So Misaki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A genuine idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to save the life of a girl I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only thing I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid... Really stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. My feelings for Misaki-chan... were those of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A dramatic death isn't befitting of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak for yourself, Yamazaki. I'm going\Nto die for my beloved Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What could be more dramatic than this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The construction has been completed, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Construction?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:14:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-kun? Satou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The construction has been completed,\Nso I guess there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to let me die a dramatic death at any cost, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you crying about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who feels like crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it almost took an hour by taxi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be morning by the time we reach the station by foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5\be1}Outside\NSignal\NRange
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll freeze to death regardless of what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an abandoned house nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandoned house?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it was built by my biological father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who gave me my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because there was a cape nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Half-baked of him, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This was my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I used it through middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first person, other than my\Nfamily, to enter this room, Satou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:17:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My stepfather would get angry if I brought friends over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warmer this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me something about yourself, Satou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll listen to whatever you have to say, no matter how boring it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about the dream I had this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A black serpent appeared out of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It fired rounds from its shiny, black gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Its broad and long sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sexual harassment warrants a fine of a million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about a story about my childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a kid, I used to play\Nbaseball at a park near my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was something like baseball, since I\Nwas using a rubber ball and a plastic bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-san, I might get married in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My folks were nagging me to do some arranged marriage meetings,\N ever since I came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I had one just for the sake of having one, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an instant bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like she was interested in me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-kun, how is your hikikomori life going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave birth to a healthy baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This luxurious house is my new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is going well in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what's with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:18:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good, no good, no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do your best, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take it easy... and make gradual progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you to\Ncome as soon as you've finished eating dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just finished eating now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you're not in a position to order me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my uncle and aunt say they feel relieved\Nwhenever I meet with you here, Satou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So did you do your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, it's kind of humiliating to be taught by Satou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-chan is a high school dropout, while I'm a college dropout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious who has the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely going to pass the University Entrance Qualification\NExam and enroll in a better college than you, Satou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right. I almost forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I also thought about my NHK meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to Satou-kun's heroics, the evil God has been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's no telling when evil will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That being the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffff80&\an8}Note: "Nihon Hitojichi Koukan-kai" translates to "Japan Hostage Exchange Association".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5\}" N.H.K. Entry... Rules of the\NHostage Exchange Association 1. The Members' own lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,\NThe "Japan Hostage Exchange Association?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Each member offers their life\Nas a hostage to the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}In short, it says "lf you die,\NI'll die too, you scoundrel!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If we do that, just like the faceoff between\Nnuclear powers during the Cold War,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}even if one wants to die, they won't be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Members will always get along...\NMembers will gather every night at Mita Park on 4th Street\NCome immediately after eating.\NI think things will probably head in a good direction...\NIt will surely be all right, I believe.\NThe penalty for breaking this agreement is ¥10,000,000,000.\NN.H.K. Chair Misaki Nakahara\NMember No.1 ( )
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Members will always get along...\NMembers will gather every night at Mita Park on 4th Street\NCome immediately after eating.\NI think things will probably head in a good direction...\NIt will surely be all right, I believe.\NThe penalty for breaking this agreement is ¥10,000,000,000.\NN.H.K. Chair Misaki Nakahara\NMember No.1 ( )
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, not a single one of our problems has been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}From here on, too, we'll probably be whispering\N"l can't, I can't" every day while we go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But still... Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I don't know how long it will hold up,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}but I'll give it a try as best I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Member No.1 (Tatsuhiro Sato )
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:21:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}N.H.K. Chair Misaki Nakahara\NMember No.1 ( Tatsuhiro Sato )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}With this, I'm sure both you and I will be okay, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Welcome to the N. H. K.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.94,0:22:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Final Episode\NWelcome to the N.H.K.!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Even if this world were going to end tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Since it's you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Would you take the curt attitude of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If so, that's okay with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.81,0:22:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}There's no need to strain yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just sometimes would be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}So lift up your face and look this way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.03,0:23:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Though it's a tiny world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}For some reason it's too big for these two hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Though it's an endless world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}For some reason it's too small for these two hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.98,0:23:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hey, I want to laugh with you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}In the irritating morning light